{"tid":2445275,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"日媒稱中方告知日方　海警船釣魚島周邊克制使用武器","createTime":"2021-03-13T13:27:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T13:49:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"74281f8d253067499f023b1130f9e8110ff36332","tid":2445275,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:27:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580432-20210313.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580432-20210313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfO6xA88r%2B4g6PmjrNIuMcHw%3D&h=68b89504\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1580432-20210313.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=cc2f433f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1580432-20210313.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n日本共同社報道，中國政府上月在《海警法》實施後，通過外交渠道告知日方，海警局艦船在尖閣諸島即中國稱的釣魚島周邊活動時，對海上保安廳巡邏船及日本漁船，將克制使用武器及強制驅逐。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述政府消息說，中方提到，海警局追蹤日本漁船，是因為漁船駛入中國領海，應對措施十分克制；中方又說，不要幻想中國會停止公務船活動。日方回應說，堅決無法接受中方公務船駛入領海。<br />\n<br />\n另外，日本防衛相岸信夫在加拿大一個視像會議，指中國海警局，在組織、裝備、人事等各方面加強與軍方協作，侵犯日本主權。"},{"pid":"d0214d7af0327166ad622225a70ec82ef65ad2a4","tid":2445275,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KovTFAW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKovTFAW.gif&h=1dd0e629&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n打撚沉你已經好克制"},{"pid":"aff6529f20a9d7ca73dc7d5e509c8e6a7db8b14c","tid":2445275,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"當你不宣而戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a455ce59d509a790e25269aac622f7a2b435b7e1","tid":2445275,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aff6529f20a9d7ca73dc7d5e509c8e6a7db8b14c","tid":2445275,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"當你不宣而戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:46:09.000Z","msg":"未經宣戰的戰爭。1907年《戰爭開始公約》第1條規定：&ldquo;締約各國承認，除非有預先的和明確無誤的警告，彼此間不應開始敵對行為。警告的形式應是說明理由的宣戰聲明或是有條件宣戰的最后通牒&rdquo;。按照這條規定，不宣而戰在法律上是非法的。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"672af6fea92062956d53cd170d1b6cb363025ecc","tid":2445275,"uid":51583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T13:49:19.000Z","msg":"係咪翠翠好多野都出事點都要搵d野拎番d威望<br />\n入面開始迫宮?"}]}